hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? paracetamol generique france * Retailers Wal-Mart Stores Inc, Macy's Inc,Kohl's Corp and Nordstrom Inc are reportingtheir second-quarter results this week. All eyes will be ontheir early reads about back-to-school sales and the outlook forthe rest of the year, with analysts expecting Wal-Mart to be aseason winner because its discount positioning can betterresonate with consumers pressured by the payroll tax rise andother economic concerns.
